CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Adamas Trust, Inc. is an internally managed real estate investment trust focused on strategically deploying capital across complementary businesses to generate durable earnings and long-term value for stockholders. Built on a foundation of strength, integrity, and resilience, NYMT combines disciplined portfolio management with an operating platform designed to capture opportunities across real estate and capital markets.
